sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant Browser as Browser (React UI)
  participant LS as localStorage
  participant API as Django API (Backend)
  participant ANA as Client Analytics (PCA/KMeans)

  User->>Browser: Open /home
  Browser->>API: GET /all-sector-stocks/timeseries/bitcoin/?symbol=^NSEI&period=3mo&interval=1d
  API-->>Browser: 200 {history...}
  Browser-->>User: Render NIFTY graph (click opens modal)

  User->>Browser: Navigate /sectors
  Browser->>API: GET /all-sector-stocks/
  API-->>Browser: 200 {data:[{sector,...}]}
  Browser-->>User: Render sector pills + insights

  User->>Browser: Open /stock/:sector
  Browser->>API: GET /all-sector-stocks/crud/stocks/?sector=<sector>
  API-->>Browser: 200 [{symbol,price,...}]
  Browser-->>User: Render sector stocks + filters

  User->>Browser: Login
  Browser->>API: POST /user/login/ (or fallback candidates)
  API-->>Browser: 200 {token/id/...}
  Browser->>LS: set current_user
  Browser-->>User: Redirect to requested page

  User->>Browser: Add To Portfolio
  Browser->>LS: update user_portfolio_stocks_v1
  Browser-->>User: Show "Added" + CTA to Portfolio

  User->>Browser: Open /portfolio
  Browser->>LS: read user_portfolio_stocks_v1
  Browser->>ANA: compute PCA projection + KMeans clusters
  ANA-->>Browser: {points, clusters}
  Browser-->>User: Render charts + Download CSV buttons

  User->>Browser: Download CSV (PCA/Clusters)
  Browser-->>User: Save file (client-side Blob)

